rows.label: qst700806_msg0002
rows.name:
Was sure this was place so secret,
friends not find in million years...

rows.label: qst700805_msg0101
rows.name: So this is where you were hiding!

rows.label: qst700805_msg0102
rows.name:
Now stop this nonsense and go
and apologize to the lady!

rows.label: qst700805_msg0201
rows.name:
Hah! I know the capital like the back of
my hand. You never stood a chance!

rows.label: qst700805_msg0202
rows.name:
Come on now. It's time to make
amends with old lady Oulu.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0301
rows.name:
Well, it seems we reduced a million
years to mere minutes.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0302
rows.name:
Now, we shall have you apologize to
the old lady, whether you like it or not.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0401
rows.name:
Should have picked a better hiding
spot. Now, go and speak to Oulu. Fast.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0501
rows.name:
This was a rather good spot, I must
admit!

rows.label: qst700805_msg0502
rows.name:
But enough playing around. Why not
go and speak to the old lady now, hm?

rows.label: qst700805_msg0601
rows.name:
I hate to break this to you, but your
little round bodies do kinda stick out.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0602
rows.name:
Anyway, are you done now? 'Cos
you need to haul yourself over to
the old woman.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0701
rows.name: Heh. You've gotta try harder than that.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0702
rows.name:
You know what else you need to
work on? Your apologies. Go and
make it up to the old lady.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0801
rows.name:
That's quite enough of your fun
and games.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0802
rows.name:
Scurry along quietly. You're going
to see Ms. Oulu, and you're going to
do it now.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0901
rows.name:
The resourcefulness of the Nopon
people never ceases to amaze me.

rows.label: qst700805_msg0902
rows.name:
Now, cease this game of cat and
mouse and go visit the lady directly.
